data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS!  If you love an extremely well cared for home as much as I do; one that's solid and built to last; and oh yes... move in ready-then this is your must-see home.  This classic, 2 story,  3 bedroom/2.5 bath home is perfect for raising a family, the person who needs rooms for hobbies or whatever, or just someone who likes elbow room.  With a charming entrance that provides privacy from everyday living, this inviting layout functions perfectly with a new A/C system, upstairs bedrooms, an extra living area and fully fenced large yard.  The familiar saying; "a place for everyone" is definitely true here.  The primary suite is Texas sized, light and bright, and features double closets and an ensuite with separate shower and tub.  Anyone work from home?  Then you'll find the downstairs light-filled study perfectly located and conducive for a work environment.  A functional kitchen with granite counters, can handle all the cooking and festivities on your calendar.  The attached roomy breakfast room allows you to see what's going on outside and participate with those in the living room.   Uniquely, you'll find the garage entered via the back valley which also boasts a greenbelt.  Talk about privacy!  And BTW, the fridge, shed in back yard, Ring security system, cameras and motion detectors, solar panels and water softener system - all convey.  I can't stress enough the care this home as received.  It's had paint touch ups, is spotless and shows so well.  We welcome you to visit this inviting home - let's make this your new home!
